creator: JosephPrince.com
descriptionHtml:
Get powerful, life-changing messages and other inspiring content on God’s grace from Joseph Prince right on your Android device! Start your day with Joseph’s Meditate Devotional, listen to his sermons on the go, and catch up on his latest videos. Get nourished by God’s Word every day and as you receive His wisdom and unconditional love, begin to reign over every challenge in life!

This app allows you to:
• Read Joseph’s daily Meditate Devotionals
• Watch the latest video messages from Joseph
• Download and stream your purchased sermons from JosephPrince.com
• Browse the sermon store and buy new sermons

For more information on Joseph Prince’s resources, please visit JosephPrince.com
descriptionShort: The official app of Joseph Prince.

title: Joseph Prince

creator: JosephPrince.com
descriptionHtml:
Get powerful, life-changing messages and other inspiring content on God’s grace from Joseph Prince across multiple devices!

As you get nourished by God’s Word every day, we believe that you will receive fresh grace and wisdom, and begin to reign over every challenge in life!

This app allows you to:
• Watch & listen to anointed messages in your Gospel Partner subscription (HD Streaming on mobile devices, Google Chromecast, Airplay).
• Connect with the Lord’s presence through a beautifully-designed daily experience with audio devotionals, guided prayers, and moments of reflection and worship.
• Find a word for what you’re going through.
• Customise your experience by adjusting playback speeds, creating your own playlists, or setting a sleep timer before bed.
• Access your purchased sermons from the official Joseph Prince website.
• Purchase sermons from the in-app sermon store.
• Download and read e-books.
• Be encouraged by powerful praise reports from people who have been impacted by the gospel of grace.

This app allows you to:

• Watch the latest video messages from Joseph
• Download and stream your purchased sermons from JosephPrince.com
